    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"690399\">Lyude</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/291565-Help/topic/How.20can.20I.20ask.20bindgen.20to.20not.20poke.20a.20.22static.20inline.22.20function/near/497759420\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>There should be a <code>--blocklist-function</code> argument that you can add to the arguments that we use with bindgen</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><code>--blocklist-function local_interrupt_enable</code> in <code>rust/bindgen_parameters</code> doesn't work.</p>",
