        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"690399\">Lyude</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/291565-Help/topic/How.20can.20I.20ask.20bindgen.20to.20not.20poke.20a.20.22static.20inline.22.20function/near/497764207\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>gotcha. can you show me it btw? I'm kind of curious what it looks like</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>branch updated, I also need to move some function into <code>spinlock.h</code> to avoid header file cyclic dependency on riscv</p>",
