    {
        "content": "<p>Ok, I find the root-cause, the macro I used is <code>#undef</code> explicityly if <code>MODULE</code> is defined, and we pass <code>-DMODULE</code> into bindgen command line. I think the code would not compile if a module is built, which is not in my test env.</p>",
